Package outputjunit.converter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssertionConverter
    Provides static methods to create JunitAssertions for JunitTestClass, JunitFieldUnderTest, JunitConstructorUnderTest and JunitMethodUnderTest.
    ConstructorConverter
    Provides a static method to convert ConstructorUnderTest to JunitConstructorUnderTest.
    FieldConverter
    Provides a static method to convert FieldUnderTest to JunitFieldUnderTest.
    MethodConverter
    Provides a static method to convert MethodUnderTest to JunitMethodUnderTest.
    PackageConverter
    Provdides static methods to convert TestPackages to a JunitPackages.
    ParameterConverter
    Provides static methods to convert ParameterUnderTest to JunitParameterUnderTest and creating Strings with the parameter types and parameter type classes
    TemplateParameterConverter
    Provides a static method to convert TemplateParameterUnderTest to JunitTemplateParameterUnderTest.
    TestClassConverter
    Provides static methods to convert TestClasses of the TestPackages in the TemporaryModel to JunitTestClasses.
